{
  "stem": "26983.10",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened-- there came so many transports from Hungaria, from Greece, some from Yugoslavia, a few partisans, and mainly from Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- and the crematorium, at that time, was so busy with gassing all the Hungarian Jews that the overflow came to the camp, and mainly to our camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here, suddenly, there was a new block of youngsters between, I would guess, 14 and 16, 17.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The kapo of this block, on block number 29, was Hans [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Erlinger. ?] I even remember his numbers-- [NON-ENGLISH], 71 302.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a Jew?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was a German or, I think, a political prisoner, but very kind and good to us children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a sick man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, he accompanied us, even, to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was extremely--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hans Erlinger. ?] And he was very kind to all of the children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he took us with the Rollwagen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so and always somebody else had to accompany us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it depends from where they come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some-- some of the children came straight from Slovakia, so they were in better condition.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember some of these children once came to us, and I asked them, from where are you, and what happened to you?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, well, we were just in the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were naked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then came Schwarzhuber.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the half of the children who were just entering the gas chambers-- said, out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He doesn't know why, but he was-- this group of children were in the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The half went in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the half, Schwarzhuber in the last moment, took out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "By the way, there was always a competition, a kind, who is a better killer, Schwarzhuber or Mengele.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All of them made selection, Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Thilo and Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Klein.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
